{"title":"石子游戏","time_limit":1000,"memory_limit":250,"url":"http://www.joyoi.cn/problem/codevs-1483","statement":[{"title":"","format":"html_final","require":["katex"],"content":"\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n题目描述\n<small>Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p><span>N</span><span>个石子放成一堆，<span>A</span>和<span>B</span>轮流操作。操作者可以投掷一枚硬币，如果正面朝上即可从堆中取出一个石子。取走最后一个石子的人赢。已知<span>A</span>有<span>P</span>的概率投出他想投的面，<span>B</span>有<span>Q</span>的概率投出他想投的面。<span>A</span>先手且假设两个人都使用必胜策略。求<span>A</span>赢的概率。</span></p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输入描述\n<small>Input Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p><span>第一行包含<span>1</span>个整数<span>N</span>和两个实数<span>P</span>，<span>Q</span>。</span></p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div  class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输出描述\n<small>Output Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p><span>输出答案，保留<span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span>位小数。</span></p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输入\n<small>Sample Input</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>1 0.5 0.5 </p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输出\n<small>Sample Output</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>0.666667 </p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n数据范围及提示\n<small>Data Size & Hint</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>对于13% 的数据, 1 &lt;= N &lt;= 10;</p>\n<p>对于100%的数据，1 &lt;= N &lt;= 99999999，0.5 &lt;= P, Q &lt;= 0.99999999且小数点后最多8位小数。</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n"}]}